Flying, ward {5}
When you cast Dezimophl, choose two opponents. When one of those players is dealt damage, the other chosen player loses life equal to the damage dealt.
[i]Soul Contract[/i] – At the beginning of each players upkeep, they may pay 3 life. If they do, they draw two cards. If you own Dezimophl, you draw a card and scry 2.
